533
00:50:40,827 --> 00:50:44,505
"'Mele Kalikimaka' is the thing to say

534
00:50:45,147 --> 00:50:47,057
"On a bright Hawaiian

535
00:50:47,292 --> 00:50:48,885
"Christmas day.

536
00:50:49,947 --> 00:50:52,020
"That's the island greeting

537
00:50:52,187 --> 00:50:55,122
"That we send to you
From the land

538
00:50:55,867 --> 00:50:58,104
"Where palm trees sway.

539
00:50:59,036 --> 00:51:00,945
"Here we know that Christmas

540
00:51:01,180 --> 00:51:02,838
"Will be green and bright

541
00:51:03,292 --> 00:51:05,463
"The sun to shine by day

542
00:51:05,628 --> 00:51:07,538
"And all the stars at night.

543
00:51:07,932 --> 00:51:11,925
"'Mele Kalikimaka' is Hawaii's way

544
00:51:12,252 --> 00:51:15,287
