570
00:53:51,557 --> 00:53:53,793
...somehow, I'm gonna prove it to you.

571
00:53:55,077 --> 00:53:58,012
Every year, he comes to our house.
I've seen him.

572
00:53:59,238 --> 00:54:00,253
