573
00:54:00,518 --> 00:54:01,795
Cross my heart.

574
00:54:05,381 --> 00:54:07,487
It's a good idea you came to stay with us.

575
00:54:07,557 --> 00:54:11,551
I love it here. You don't gotta put on
your coat to go to the bathroom.

576
00:54:11,718 --> 00:54:14,436
