590
00:55:38,058 --> 00:55:39,651
No. Not in the mood.

591
00:55:41,164 --> 00:55:42,789
What are you looking at?

592
00:55:45,164 --> 00:55:48,197
The silent majesty of a winter's morn.
The clean...

593
00:55:48,363 --> 00:55:50,370
