I'd like to get something for you, Clark.

641
00:59:09,303 --> 00:59:11,692
Something really nice.

642
00:59:28,663 --> 00:59:30,387
Is your house on fire, Clark?

643
00:59:30,616 --> 00:59:32,558
No Bethany, those are Christmas lights.

644
00:59:32,632 --> 00:59:34,355
Don't throw me down, Clark.

645
00:59:34,456 --> 00:59:35,732
I'll try not to.

646
00:59:36,376 --> 00:59:38,132
Is this the airport?

647
00:59:38,392 --> 00:59:39,570
We're here!

648
00:59:39,673 --> 00:59:43,088
Me and Bethany figured out
the perfect gift for you.

649
00:59:43,193 --> 00:59:45,910
Uncle Louis, you didn't have to
buy me anything.

650
00:59:45,977 --> 00:59:48,213
Damn it, Bethany, he guessed it.

651
00:59:48,857 --> 00:59:50,383
