678
01:01:23,806 --> 01:01:24,505
Lime.

679
01:01:24,958 --> 01:01:26,365
It's her Jell-O mold.

680
01:01:26,430 --> 01:01:30,456
I'll take it, Eddie. Go into
the living room and enjoy yourself.

681
01:01:33,598 --> 01:01:35,256
Let's go find your sister.

682
01:01:55,616 --> 01:01:56,728
