690
01:02:39,938 --> 01:02:41,280
"I pledge allegiance...

691
01:02:41,506 --> 01:02:45,019
"...to the flag of
the United States of America...

692
01:02:45,442 --> 01:02:47,035
"...and to the republic...

693
01:02:47,266 --> 01:02:51,357
"...for which it stands,
one nation under God, indivisible...

694
01:02:51,906 --> 01:02:55,103
"...with liberty and justice for all."

695
01:02:57,187 --> 01:02:57,886
Amen.

696
01:03:03,907 --> 01:03:07,683
Catherine, if this turkey tastes
half as good as it looks...

697
01:03:07,908 --> 01:03:10,396
