It's good.

713
01:05:36,652 --> 01:05:38,310
What's wrong with the dog?

714
01:05:41,836 --> 01:05:46,407
He's just yackin' on a bone.
He's got it up. He's all right now.

715
01:05:48,139 --> 01:05:50,596
Maybe if you wouldn't feed him
from the table...

716
01:05:52,077 --> 01:05:53,670
No.

717
01:05:54,477 --> 01:05:57,346
He's probably just nosing
through the trash.

718
01:06:07,085 --> 01:06:09,354
If you're not doing anything constructive...

719
01:06:09,421 --> 01:06:11,942
