739
01:09:13,847 --> 01:09:15,789
- Dad's gonna flip out.
- Nobody's gonna flip out.

740
01:09:15,863 --> 01:09:18,230
We're gonna have a wonderful Christmas.

741
01:09:21,656 --> 01:09:22,998
What the hell do you want?

742
01:09:23,064 --> 01:09:25,748
I have a delivery for Clark W. Griswold.

743
01:09:25,912 --> 01:09:28,051
I was supposed to deliver it yesterday...

744
01:09:28,184 --> 01:09:32,341
